summary: WIP- Adds the island of Artaeum into the game. Later versions will add quests and more buildings/NPCs.
descriptionHtml:
Welcome, to Artaeum.
As you may know, Artaeum was the island of the Psiijic order long ago before the island suddenly vanished. This mod adds Artaeum to the game. Right now, it is just an island with a few buildings, but I wanted to get this out there so people can expect it. 
NOTE: . If you want to visit Artaeum, go into the console and type in Coc ArtaeumExterior13
Then you can roam around. Have some fun running around and stuff.

Features:
__________
A new island with 3 new npc. Adds a few buildings. 
Has an inn where you can rent a bed. I built the scripts from the ground up (it was hard). Partially works right now, I will definitely work on it.
Has a trader named Jensen who sells \"potions, scrolls and arcane secrets\"
Has a trainer near Jensen named Victun. He can train you to level 75 Destruction.

Bugs:
__________
You can change your rooms with the inn, so you can switch from the half room to the whole combo room at anytime, but you still pay the fee.

Next update will be on: Unknown, Finals has been really tough
 March 18, 2012
Next update will include:
__________
Voice acting
New quests
Many NPCs
Many traders
New buildings and a way to get to Artaeum
Credits: 
__________
G-d for making the world and us.
Bethesda for making Skyrim and the CK
Me for thinking of this idea.
My team for voice acting help.
